ive insights as to how space-time\nrotation parameters encode information pertaining to the inertial effects in\nthe corresponding fluid dual.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Feb 2020 06:46:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Aug 2020 04:33:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-07"}
