rt). Extensive experiments are conducted on\nboth PGM and I-RAVEN datasets, showing that our SRAN outperforms the\nstate-of-the-art models by a considerable margin.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Feb 2020 08:44:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 21 Dec 2020 08:46:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 7 Jun 2022 11:49:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-08"}
