2 Ising\ndiamond and tetrahedral chains is an essential prerequisite for observation of\na relevant pseudo-critical behavior in a close vicinity of their ground-state\nphase boundary.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Feb 2020 13:13:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-17"}
